article_title: Aetna CEO Says Obamacare An 'Attractive Growth Opportunity'

article_metadata.author: Bruce Japsen

og.description: Health insurer Aetna (AET) said it would make more money than originally anticipated thanks to “attractive growth” from new enrollment on public exchanges under the Affordable Care Act. Aetna now expects its 2015 earnings per share of “at least $7.00” compared to an earlier projection of at least “$6.90” per share, [...]
